Hair Package is not just a monthly subscription to lavish you with hand-picked, high-quality hair products… We are a community dedicated to helping inspire women to embrace what makes them uniquely beautiful! 
Not only do we send our members the best hair products for their curly hair needs, but we spread a contagious message of self-love. 
The products you’ll find in our box are handmade by small business owners. We choose to partner with these entrepreneurs because we feel they provide a personalized touch you won't get with bigger brands. We believe it is vital to support local businesses and invest in entrepreneurship. 
Joining our community means you will be inspired month after month to unbox your natural beauty!

Alright guys so after over 12 months of perfecting the products the concept and the branding my new company has finally launched! Unlimited socks and undies is a monthly socks and underwear subscription delivered to your door! If your anything like I was then finding a pair of socks became a mission in itself and then keeping up with the washing underwear washing was hard! And how many of us have a socks and undies draw full of things that really need throwing out, but we hang onto them because we know at some stage we will get caught out and have to wear them! I've never heard anyone say they easily find socks and you can never have to many! So here it is.. Unlimited socks and undies! Premium products delivered cheaper than retail! Subscribe now!
